      <h2>The Bottom Line Up Front</h2>
      <p>No supplement — peptides, creatine, testosterone support, whatever's trending this month — overrides the two non-negotiables for building muscle after 40: <strong>consistent resistance training and enough daily protein.</strong> Supplements are multipliers. They amplify a system that's already working. If the foundation isn't there, you're spending money to optimize something that isn't built yet.</p>
